videos.headline: Patterson takes 1st play 81 yards for TD
videos.description: Jaret Patterson puts Buffalo on the board first, ripping off an 81-yard touchdown run on the Bulls' first play from scrimmage.

videos.headline: Patterson rips off 35-yard TD run on 4th down
videos.description: Buffalo goes for it on 4th-and-3 and Jaret Patterson bursts through the line, breaks a tackle and races 35 yards for the touchdown.
